Hey all,

Thank you to everyone that attended the Reclaim Your Time With AI workshop today! If you weren't able to join us or would like a refresher on the content, I've included a link to the recording here<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4BTkWL_GOkk>
and attached a PDF of the presentation for reference. We have access to this recording for one week, so if you'd like to review, please feel free to do so by 4/17.

If you have any questions, please reach out. Have a great rest of the week!

Thanks,


