<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4BTkWL_GOkk">recording here</a> </span><span style="display:none"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif">and attached a PDF of the presentation for reference. We have access to this recording for one week, so if you&#8217;d like to review, please feel free to do so by 4/17.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif">If you have any questions, please reach out. Have a great rest of the week!<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
